text: Dmytro Prosvirnin (born 7 January 1967) is a Ukrainian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Ukraine Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:People from Vorokhta
